OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy for most with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain, locally heavy at first.
OL,7,FBecoming brighter from the west with
OL,8,Fshowers in the south. Windy, with
OL,9,Fcoastal gales in the southwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FTonight, showers easing as
OL,12,Frain clears northeast. Turning drier
OL,13,Fwith clear spells developing. Winds
OL,14,Feasing overnight, though wetter,
OL,15,Fwindier conditions return in the west
OL,16,Fthrough the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
