OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FHazy sunshine in the south and
OL,6,Fsoutheast. Rain in the west, sometimes
OL,7,Fheavy with thunder, pushing
OL,8,Fsoutheastwards. Windy around coasts.
OL,9,FCool in the west; warmer in the east.
